===============
 zope.hookable
===============

.. image:: https://img.shields.io/pypi/v/zope.hookable.svg
        :target: https://pypi.python.org/pypi/zope.hookable/
        :alt: Latest release

.. image:: https://img.shields.io/pypi/pyversions/zope.hookable.svg
